# /deploy-win

Deploy the Cinema app to the Windows machine via the sql-bridge API at `http://100.94.185.70:8765`.

Run these steps in order. Stop if any step fails and report the error.

## Step 1 — Stop the app

```bash
curl -sf -X POST http://100.94.185.70:8765/stop
```

Report whether the app was stopped or was already not running.

## Step 2 — Pull latest changes

```bash
curl -sf -X POST http://100.94.185.70:8765/git-pull
```

Show the git output. Fail if `success` is false.

## Step 3 — Build the solution

```bash
curl -sf --max-time 120 -X POST http://100.94.185.70:8765/build
```

Report success or show the build errors. Fail if `success` is false.

## Step 4 — Start the app

```bash
curl -sf -X POST http://100.94.185.70:8765/start
```

Report the app URL and PID on success. Show the error on failure.

After all steps succeed, confirm the deployment is complete.
